title: I'm Alan Partridge - series 1
description:
A 1997 British television series with Steve Coogan playing Alan Partridge a spoof presenter, who having lost his television chat show, is now reduced to night time radio where he continues to offend his audience.

The fly on the wall look at his failed career produces some classic comedy moments with the staff of the Linton Travel Tavern, his obsession with Bankok ladyboys and his attempts to relieve his boredom.

Review of the series on imdb gives a rating of 9.3/10.

Six half hour episodes in divx format.
